<user-memory-input>Remember that this the main goal of this repo is actually to create a maven plugin which will be imported into the main nx repo. The maven plugin should integrate maven into Nx in such a way where nx is able to execute maven commands exactly as maven executes them. The plugin should read from the maven official apis as much as possible so that maven's understanding of the workspace is reflected into Nx.</user-memory-input>
